---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | A1 Service Expert"
  description="Terms and conditions for A1 Service Expert car servicing and repair services in Kettering, Northamptonshire."
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="prose prose-slate mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: November 2025</p>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        These terms and conditions govern your use of our services at A1 Service Expert. By engaging our services, you agree to be bound by these terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">2. Services</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        A1 Service Expert provides vehicle servicing, repairs, diagnostics, and maintenance services. All work is carried out by qualified technicians using appropriate tools and equipment.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>Services are performed in accordance with manufacturer specifications where applicable</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to refuse service if we believe the work is beyond our capabilities or equipment</li>
        <li>Additional work may be identified during service or repair; we will contact you for authorization before proceeding</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">3. Quotes and Pricing</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>Quotes provided are estimates based on the information available at the time</li>
        <li>Final costs may vary if additional work is required or parts pricing changes</li>
        <li>We will inform you of any significant changes to the quoted price before proceeding</li>
        <li>All prices include VAT at the current rate unless otherwise stated</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">4. Payment Terms</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>Payment is due upon collection of the vehicle unless alternative arrangements have been agreed in writing</li>
        <li>We accept cash, debit cards, and credit cards</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to retain the vehicle until payment is received in full</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">5. Warranty</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Parts and labour are warranted as follows:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>Parts: Covered by manufacturer warranty (typically 12 months)</li>
        <li>Labour: 12 months from date of completion</li>
        <li>Warranty does not cover wear and tear, misuse, or damage caused by factors outside our control</li>
        <li>Warranty is void if subsequent work on the same components is carried out by a third party</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">6. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>You are responsible for providing accurate information about your vehicle and its history</li>
        <li>You must inform us of any known faults or previous repairs</li>
        <li>Personal belongings left in vehicles are your responsibility; we accept no liability for loss or damage</li>
        <li>Vehicles must be collected within 7 days of work completion</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">7. Liability</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        Our liability is limited as follows:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>We maintain comprehensive insurance for our business operations</li>
        <li>Our liability for any claim is limited to the cost of the service or repair in question</li>
        <li>We are not liable for consequential losses such as loss of earnings or alternative transport costs</li>
        <li>Nothing in these terms limits our liability for death or personal injury caused by negligence</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">8. Cancellation</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>You may cancel a booking with reasonable notice</li>
        <li>If work has commenced, you will be charged for work completed and parts ordered</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to charge a cancellation fee for late cancellations</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">9. Data Protection</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        We process personal data in accordance with UK data protection laws. Please see our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">10. Disputes</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base text-slate-700">
        <li>We aim to resolve any concerns promptly and professionally</li>
        <li>Please contact us directly to discuss any issues</li>
        <li>These terms are governed by English law and subject to the jurisdiction of English courts</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-black">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. The latest version will always be available on our website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-black">Contact Information</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-slate-700">
        <p><strong>A1 Service Expert</strong></p>
        <p>11 Cunliffe Dr, Kettering NN16 8LD</p>
        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:07394433889" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">07394 433889</a></p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@a1serviceexpert.com" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">support@a1serviceexpert.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
